parameters:
Clea: Eisa-san, I came here on a request from the Merchant
Guild's Nurse-san.

Clea: We are not enemies. Let's go back together to our
fellow members of the Merchant Guild.
Merchant Eisa: ...Are you also part of it?

Merchant Eisa: This fabric that emits such a beautiful
sheen... and the comfortable feeling of gently enveloping
the skin...

Merchant Eisa: I will absolutely not give it to anyone,
anyone, anyone, anyone!

Clea: It seems that persuading with words is impossible.
Let's make them obedient even if we have to do it
forcefully.
Clea: It seems like she has fainted.

Mage Relm: There must be something wrong with these
dangerously obsessed clothes!

Priestess Sophia: It's a pity, but should we undress her?
Nora-chan, can I ask for your cooperation?
Clea: Let's deliver it to Nurse-san.

events.name: EV002華麗なるギャンブラー1-5

parameters: Do you want to enter the boss area?
Clea (Let's prepare first before doing that)

The man who was chased by the Chronos Thieves, 'Somehow I
managed to shake off my pursuers... thanks to that, I ended
up in a place like this.'

The man who was chased by the organization called Mucos:
'No, the organization has a long reach, especially that guy
called Cors. He's a man as tenacious as a snake.'
Fuego with the hawk eyes: Oh, do you know Cors?

The man who was chased by the Chronos Thieves: Oh, you're
Fuego with the hawk eyes!

Fuego with the hawk eyes: I'm honored that you know about
me.
Fuego with the hawk eyes: May I ask you all a favor?
Clea: What will happen to these people?

Fuego with the hawk eyes: My subordinates will come to
collect them.
Hey, please stop progressing the conversation on your own.

Priestess Sophia: Cors-san... I see, so they were defectors
from the organization.

Cors the Wanderer: Half of that is correct, so let me take
charge here--

Cors the Wanderer: That's a clever greeting! Are you
preparing to return to active duty as a combatant?

Fuego with the hawk eyes: My crushed eye doesn't feel so
good...! I didn't hear anything about gouging out both of
your eyes!

Cors the Wanderer: It's a matter of the organization's
reputation, so I'm sorry, but could you all quietly return
to Oros?

Fuego with the hawk eyes: We also have our pride, and I
don't have any personal grudge against you!

Clea: Let's hand them over to the guards as a compromise. If
we, who happened to pass by, catch them, it should save face
for us.

Mage Relm: Sigh... Normally, you don't say that after
getting punched.

Cors the Wanderer: Hawk eyes... Let's settle this here.
These people are the kind who would kill dragons.

Fuego with the hawk eyes: I understand... They're the kind
of people who would defeat an invincible iron mask, so it's
fine.
Thief Nora: So you know Cors-san?

Fuego with the hawk eyes: It's a story from a long time ago
when we could fight without any positions or anything.

Fuego with the hawk eyes: Clea-san, this is our client.
Could you please give us a heads up before you start hitting
them?

Clea: I understand, but I don't think we can avoid calling
out to them.

Fuego with the hawk eyes: I have prepared something that
seems useful for our adventure as an additional reward.
